high_descs: Turn right and walk up to the bathtub
Pick up the right most candle from the edge of the bathtub
Turn right to face toward the toilet
Put the candle on top of the back of the toilet
Turn to look back at the bathtub
Pick up the nearest candle on the edge of the bathtub
Turn to face the toilet
Put the candle on top of the back of the toilet
anns.task_desc: Put the candles on the toilet

high_descs: Turn to your right toward the bathtub
Pick the candle on the right from the tub bar
Turn around to face the toilet flush and raise the candle
Put the candle on the flush tank
Turn around to the tub and face the second candle
Put the second candle from tub bar
Go back to face the flush toilet
Put the candle behind the first candle on the flush tank
anns.task_desc: Put two scent candles on the flush tank

high_descs: Turn right and go to the tub.
Pick up the candle to the left of the bottle.
Turn left and go to the toilet.
Put the candle on the back of the toilet.
Turn right and go to the tub.
Pick up the candle on the edge of the tub.
Turn back to the toilet.
Put the candle on the back of the toilet behind the blue spray bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put two candles on the back of the toilet.
